<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Your Pokémon for Today</title>
    <link href='/css/style.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png">
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class='page-container'>

      <div class='intro-container'>
        <h1>Your Pokémon for Today</h1>

        {% if stats.remaining > 0 %}
          <p><a href='http://kcgreendotcom.com/'>KC Green</a> is <span class="what-is-kc">a very talented artist</span> who keeps drawing Pokémon. Many have tried to stop him, but none have succeeded.</p>
        {% else %}
          <p><a href='http://kcgreendotcom.com/'>KC Green</a> is <span class="what-is-kc">a very talented artist</span> who went and drew all the Pokémon. You can't stop him now, it's far too late.</p>
        {% endif %}

        <p>Follow KC on <a href='http://twitter.com/kcgreenn'>Twitter</a> and <a href='http://midnitesurprise.com/'>Tumblr</a> and patronise him on <a href='http://www.patreon.com/kcgreen'>Patreon</a>.</p>

        {% if stats.remaining > 0 %}
          <p>Wanna see what Pokémon might appear here tomorrow? Check out <a href="/tomorrow/">Your Pokémon For Tomorrow</a>!</p>
        {% endif %}

        <p class='text-muted'><small>Site by <a href='http://twitter.com/blimpage'>Pat McKenna</a>. Code's <a href='http://github.com/blimpage/your-pokemon-for-today'>on GitHub</a> if you want it. Last updated {{build_date}}.</small></p>
      </div>

      <div class='pokemon-container'>
        {% include "templates/gallery.njk" %}
      </div>

    </div>

    <script src='/js/scripts.min.js'></script>
  </body>
</html>
